				<header class="single-article-header">

					<h1 class="post-title clear">Kim Jong-un fighting for life after &#8216;heart surgery&#8217; as North Korea battles coronavirus</h1><div class="comments-top-cta clearfix">
	<a href="#metro-comments-container" class="metro-comments-cta" data-track="view-comments-top">
