				<div class="article-body">

					<figure class="alignnone img-container shareable-item" style="max-width:540px"><div class="img-wrap">
<a id="share-item-12337249-399" class="anchor"></a><div class="item-share-buttons item-share">
<a class="share-item share-item-facebook btn" title="Share this on Facebook" data-track="share-item-facebook"><span class="icon icon-facebook"></span></a><a class="share-item share-item-twitter btn" target="_blank" title="Share this on Twitter" data-track="share-item-twitter" rel="noopener"><span class="icon icon-twitter"></span></a><a class="share-item share-item-pinterest btn" target="_blank" title="Share this on Pinterest" data-track="share-item-pinterest" rel="noopener"><span class="icon icon-pinterest"></span></a>
</div>
<img width="644" height="429" data-rsz="shrink" src="https://i1.wp.com/metro.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/PRI_144457816.jpg?quality=90&amp;strip=all&amp;zoom=1&amp;resize=644%2C429&amp;ssl=1" alt="North Korean leader Kim Jong Un visits a drill of long-range artillery sub-units of the Korean People's Army, in North Korea in this image released by North Korea's Korean Central News Agency (KCNA) on March 2, 2020.?KCNA?via REUTERS ATTENTION EDITORS - THIS IMAGE WAS PROVIDED BY A THIRD PARTY. REUTERS IS UNABLE TO INDEPENDENTLY VERIFY THIS IMAGE. NO THIRD PARTY SALES. SOUTH KOREA OUT. NO COMMERCIAL OR EDITORIAL SALES IN SOUTH KOREA." class="wp-image-12337249">
</div>
<figcaption>North Korean dictator Kim Jong-un is reported to be gravely ill in hospital after undergoing surgery for an undisclosed condition (Picture: Reuters)</figcaption></figure><p>North Korean leader Kim Jong-un is gravely-ill after undergoing heart surgery, it has been claimed.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.cnn.com/2020/04/20/politics/kim-jong-un-north-korea/index.html">CNN</a> reported that the 36 year-old leaderâs condition is being monitored by US intelligence officials, who were reportedly told that Kim was âin grave dangerâ after the cardiovascular operation. Kim was absent from North Koreaâs most important annual holiday on April 15, raising speculation about his well-being.</p>
<p>South Korean news website the Daily NK claimed earlier on Monday night that Kim was âmostly-recoveredâ from the procedure. The website obtained the story from a single anonymous informant based in North Korea, and has been unable to obtain further details on Kimâs condition, <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-04-21/kim-surgery-report-fuels-speculation-about-north-korean-leader?srnd=premium">Bloomberg</a> reported.</p>
<div class="vjs-video-container vjs-fixed vjs-responsive">

